<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ol>
      <li><p>24 more. Sample responses:</p><ul>
<li>
<m>82-20 = 62</m> <m>62-4 = 58</m> </li>
<li>
<m>58 + 2</m> <m>60 + 20</m> <m>80 + 2</m> <m>2 + 20 + 2</m>
</li>
</ul>
      </li>
      <li><p>38 more. Sample responses:</p><ul>
<li>
<m>20 + 10 = 30</m> <m>9 + 5 = 14</m> <m>30 +14 = 44</m> <m>82-40 = 42</m> <m>42-4 = 38</m> </li>
<li><m>82-(29 + 15)</m></li>
</ul>
      </li>
      <li><p>53 fewer. Sample responses:</p><ul>
<li>
<m>82 -20 = 62</m> <m>62 -2 = 60</m> <m>60-7 = 53</m> </li>
<li>
<m>29 + 1</m> <m>30 + 50</m> <m>80 + 2</m> <m>1 + 50 + 2</m>
</li>
</ul>
      </li>
      <li><p>14 fewer. Sample response:</p><ul>
<li>
<m>20 + 10 = 30</m> <m>9 + 5 = 14</m> <m>30 + 14 = 44</m> <m>58-44 = 14</m> </li>
<li><m>58- (15 + 29)</m></li>
</ul>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </solution>


