  <!-- Launch -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="launch-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Groups of 2</li>
      <li>
        <q>¿Qué tipos de plantas ven cuando caminan a casa desde la escuela?</q>  (Trees. Bushes. Flowers. Vines.)
      </li>
      <li>Share responses.</li>
    </ul>
  </paragraphs>


  <!-- Instrucciones para el desarrollo de la actividad -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="instructions-teacher-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Display the graph.</li>
      <li>
        <q>Trabajen individualmente para resolver los problemas usando la gráfica. Si les ayuda, pueden usar la rutina ‘Tres lecturas’</q>
      </li>
      <li>7–10 minutes: independent work time</li>
      <li><p>Monitor for students who solve the one-step problems by:</p><ul>
<li>using the bars on the graph to count up to or back from one number to another.</li>
<li>using equations to show adding or subtracting by place.</li>
</ul>
      </li>
      <li><p>Monitor for students who solve two-step problems by:</p><ul>
<li>adding two numbers then subtracting the sum from another number.</li>
<li>subtracting a number, then subtracting again from the difference.</li>
</ul>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </paragraphs>

